label: A2BC3_cP24_213_c_a_d-001
title: Al$_{2}$Mo$_{3}$C Structure
comments:
This is a ``filled'' \href{current_web_home_dir/A_cP20_213_cd-001}{$\beta$-Mn (A13) structure}, with the aluminum and molybdenum atoms almost exactly on the sites of the manganese atoms in A13. 
 This structure may also be found in the enantiomorphic space group $P4_{3}32$ \#212.
